column5: I was just wondering if there were any guests on here, past or present, from our place...if so let's talk fish!Colin

Hello, Have never been there, but met a guy at LS Outposts 2 yrs ago, Nate was his name. he had nothing but good things to say about that place and you as well. saw some videos he posted on trophy-clips.com, great videos of all of you at moosehorn. I was at LS the day he caught that 57 1/2" BEAST. Wow, what a fish!
